CONFIGURATION FOR REMOTE RING ZL-03

1	Connect Kobo to computer.
	2	In Finder/Documents open disk Kobo.
	(3	On Macbook: Press Cmd + Shift + ., to display hidden files)
	4	Open folder .kobo, then Kobo.
	5	Open file "Kobo eReader.conf" in TextEdit.
	6	Find section [DeveloperSettings].

If it is there:
ForceWifiOn=true

If it is not there input on the end:
[DeveloperSettings]
ForceWifiOn=true


	7	Save file.
	8	Safely eject your Kobo.
	9 	Disconnect the cable and restart the reader.
